flowRoot.flowPara: The window closes after all of these operations have completed.
Find bar slides down from below the header bar.

The action bar at the bottom is intended to make the document and image viewers closely related to the Files app - they play a previewing role, which helps to identify a file before performing an operation on it. However, the action bar does detract from using the viewers as viewers - it is a distraction if the user doesn't want to perform a file operation. One option might be to allow hiding the action bar, or only show it on hover/tap (like the zoom controls):
